item.title: Create A Useless AI
item.description: Introduction RoughlyRoughtly six months ago, I started on a journey. A journey journeyjourneyjourny of epic sword fights, great victories, and even more significant losses For some context, my school partakes in a statewide program STLP The Program itself is a massive science fair/club; you can read more about it in the link above The plan It was simple, make an app that is helpful to the student population The Idea Was to make an app for mental help; the goal was a Therapy app that students could download on their phones or access using our web page.
